REST API:

/lessons/:ID
    - GET return lessons (return comments just on ID)
    - POST create new lessons

/lessons/learned/:ID
    - GET return learnedlessons (return comments just on ID)
    - POST add to learned lessons
    - PUT add rating or comment to lesson

/ranking
    - GET return ranking list of users



DOCUMENTATION:
you can just modify the query in the DAL for returning just lessons created by the user